<plot>Devastated by the suicide of her daughter, Becky Douglas, a suburban Atlanta housewife, travels to India to honor her memory. During her trip, Becky is horrified at the plight of the leprosy-afflicted and joins forces with Indian dignitary Padma Venkataraman to eradicate the disease and its stigma.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?082366</url></doc>
